#: ../../source/index.rst:17 0a2b815062ea4363a526008339f984ab
msgid "TensorMesh: The Modern FEM Library 🚀"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/index.rst:19 8a1cad6d8ba0457288bd9d66f766ce49
msgid ""
"A fast 🚀, differentiable 🎯, cross-platform 💻, JIT-free 📌, and debugging-"
"friendly 🚨 finite element library that prioritizes user experience "
"through clean, Pythonic APIs 🤗"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/index.rst:21 7c15f18a9d1c41aead6ba87c7f9a6e9f
msgid ""
"TensorMesh is a modern finite element method (FEM) library built on "
"PyTorch, designed to solve partial differential equations (PDEs) with "
"elegance and efficiency. By seamlessly integrating with PyTorch's "
"ecosystem, it provides automatic differentiation and GPU acceleration "
"while maintaining an intuitive, Pythonic interface."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/index.rst:25 166c37a7ea7c47389537d7291183e620
msgid "Core Strengths"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/index.rst:27 dd8aa1a1f2d34eaa9058f4069604e7dc
msgid ""
"**Easy to Use**: Clean, intuitive Pythonic APIs that make FEM accessible "
"to both beginners and experts"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/index.rst:28 bab65eb881e04572a3ed61c64d10086f
msgid ""
"**Easy to Debug**: Clear error messages and straightforward execution "
"flow for painless debugging"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/index.rst:29 7c9148e6a66e446fb284d778eac998ff
msgid ""
"**Cross Platform**: Works seamlessly across Windows, Linux, and macOS "
"without complex dependencies"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/index.rst:30 4c186f2b720349ffa68829cf2771517a
msgid ""
"**Seamless PyTorch Integration**: Leverage PyTorch's powerful automatic "
"differentiation and GPU acceleration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/index.rst:31 87b8412a4d05408ba3907c26718ebae4
msgid ""
"**Comprehensive Element Support**: Work with a wide range of elements "
"including triangular, tetrahedral, pyramid, and prismatic types"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/index.rst:32 b8b6f50705b045f795d6a20a50dfa864
msgid ""
"**High-Performance Assembly**: Optimized element assembly operations for "
"both CPU and GPU architectures"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/index.rst:33 64322222200a43ac90d322375a09368b
msgid ""
"**Advanced Solvers**: Efficient sparse matrix solvers with flexible "
"backend options (PETSc, PyTorch)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/index.rst:34 5d1a3361b9ac4404ad687eed9b6c4a49
msgid ""
"**Rich Visualization**: Integrated tools for mesh and solution "
"visualization"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/index.rst:35 c2a878619fff4670a828af47208eb35b
msgid ""
"**Smart Mesh Generation**: Automated mesh generation for common "
"geometries with intelligent defaults"
msgstr ""

